HIGH TEA DELIVERY?!
Cant imagine myself having Afternoon High Tea: Cass Edition (2pax SGD 88) at home with delivery from Intercontinental Singapore! Comes with Scones, Savory, Sweets and TWG loose tea, think interesting items such as:
.
1️⃣ Lychee Rose Macaron ⭐️

Prawn Mousse Pita ⭐️
4️⃣ Feta Cheese Cranberry Roll with dried fruits and nuts
.
📍Intercontinental Singapore (Lobby Lounge)
📞 6825 1008
#StayHome #StayHomeSG #StayAtHome #CircuitBreaker #SGunited
